{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"清若芷萱","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaEIJNapj1ibLnckBHdMF2pbTnMtdF32UHoBS2qCrd6PeWxAUxf4yk54MhicSEib9dcvXWdFibbRh3ict7BQ/0","content":"认知一致，对方只是做不到，在能上欠缺","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":9051,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492785656000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"小怪兽","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay2NAAUg9kUxdbW1e5JFVDsYsiag0wfPGibtXN1jjcRBciasJq3jTQI2FaZvico9652VyzqWJ7Uwgy7cW/0","content":"<p>我作为下属，认为，我的上级<br>1.处理好与ta自己领导的关系，<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">正确</span>领会上级的思路，方向。<br>2.与同级搞好协调互助工作<br>3.制定本部门工作计划，策略。关注本部门工作的重点，关键点，把握进度。培养下属。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":9007,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492778883000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"千幽","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98UNjBmKBWOicOVxDToZOY3YjGpQ0Lr8Wy7tKu4DFX9VWNBBD6vTeV18n7EqwV3cGJ5vWNj2QfwXTlN3tVBzmHnwl/0","content":"<p>我的上司身份是多合一，他即是产品总监，也是研发总监，还是公司副总和股东。</p><p>（要求、边界、重要性）</p><p>我认为他的角色中，最重要有两件事。</p><p>第一是以前瞻性的眼光带领产品和研发走向一个靠谱的方向。毕竟我们是一个新行业，同行也都是在摸索。我们员工整天埋头做事，主要工作是落实想法，又不像老板总能接触外界人与事，难免对行业的把握不够全面。这个时候应该是总监+副总来给予我们方向上的指引。</p><p>第二是管理好团队里二十多个人。现在大家都觉得虽然有上级，但是跟没上级一样，希望他能够更多的关心下属，知道如何激励下属更好的完成工作，帮助下属提升职业技能等，建立起一个更加优秀的团队。</p><p>不应该做的事情有一件，就是以他的角色来说，不应该再总亲自投入到编码、查bug、测试中去了，希望他用这些时间做性价比更高的事情，同时培养好他的下属去处理这类事情。<br></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8978,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492773092000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"敏","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay36u84xJJa5xZVbSorVQsjiaRtdKff23d2pibDW0oSbVW3r0CUiaQtIg47Itf131L8acNXmLucqib4ibt/0","content":"<p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">试着用上次和老板的对话来说明。</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">老板：你应当有工作主动性，积极的去改进工作，自已找活做。</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">下属：我已经将份内事做得足够好了。再去改进工作，需要部门间的沟通，超出了职责范围。</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">老板：你应当要能主动和其它部门沟通。我授权你。</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><br></span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">老板认为我的角色：</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">1.做好本部门职责内的事，是应当的。</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">2.承担别部门领导交办的事，是应当的。</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">3.积极和别部门沟通协调，是应当的。</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><br></span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">我认为我的角色：</span></font></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: '\\\\601D源黑体cn', 'Helvetica Neue';\">1.做好本部门职责内的事，是应当的。</span></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">2.承担别部门领导交办的事，是应当的。</span></font></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: '\\\\601D源黑体cn', 'Helvetica Neue'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">3.别部门沟通协调，是领导的职责。</span><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><br></span></font></p><p>最后沟通的结果，其它部门的业务层由我去沟通。其它部门的领导层，由领导去沟通。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8813,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492737098000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"浅紫","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay5Qias5Y6BOJq0bibrmkolNJFtbyicK1y9rN41JY4SIw04awshr8lhByygakZc9SVzOfPej1XNTbShq/0","content":"待补充","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8704,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492702352000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"神韵-Albert Han","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaELzmFHR1I2ZjVCx4aCrH9WAreVavWYKrT6hxPRmg4JicPIewicOfdBoxuhhSCnfDmEoev1COg0np4wQ/0","content":"我是下属，对应的社会角色是老板，老板思想比较激进，也能跟随时代潮流，甚至引领行业的时代潮流，个人主观性非常强，他的角色认知是指明大方向，其他全部由我这个下属部署安排，平时也不会纠错，以结果为导向，结果不另其满意就会大发雷霆，所以需要跟老板沟通我们两人彼此的角色定位。<div>关于老板的角色定位，我告知老板我的观点：</div><div>一、指明方向，根据其在行业的丰富阅历和对时代潮流的把握，确立下一步的发展方向。</div><div>二、制定“真正”的目标，按照SMART原则制定目标，而非一个宽泛的表述。</div><div>三、结果导向，过程把控。平时多多与下属交流，帮助下属及早发现问题，从而提高效率。<br><div><br></div></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8632,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492694101000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"stella\uD83D\uDD25","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaSicyupTSzFbVyoQhw811sPFadF2iaOsPXQ9eozl1e8WcgV3zu0YNXrAyFrOH2TCFPBF6WxhJV7Y21u/0","content":"<p>作为老板：</p><p>1、把握公司发展的大方向，定目标</p><p>2、与下属多沟通，了解工作中遇到的困难点，帮助修正目标或者提高下属能力</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8376,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492659274000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"千利休","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJBkpIkVNa5FLhE0qcn4hibdztDwoFibnREIiamouUibBWIibIuvQwXtQldXFBkHiaZCym1ez0DoM1zRgTl8MvT5HmVFa/0","content":"当我是妻子的时候，原则上，我认为我的丈夫应该与我平分家务劳动、对孩子的照顾与经济收入。在对方遇挫时期，予以恰当的心灵支持。但要根据具体情况，做出细微的调整。例如，在家务上，根据各人的特长，区分任务。再或，其中一方正处于事业关键期，压力大时间紧，家务即短期向另一方倾斜。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8283,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492650829000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"疏影","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaS8DS09Y7uHlpQ1xDicSZk2ot00sBg4sQXgYg8lGp9EbSVXAo0G7D54Fuov2d85GibKYXwMpsVKicxEt/0","content":"对于丈夫：情绪稳定，有效沟通。不随意指责别人，关心孩子，家庭财务透明。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8225,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492643036000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"张梦路","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZaLoY2RXU5FZibDrTsS1osmryDqKeuAvlF9licJ4nKDicnJ1HjwXTbvxdlVJj5oBJgqhR72iaGMxLcib1jJGsyWnUnj/0","content":"<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 32px;\">父母、孩子</span><div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 32px;\">如果我是父母，我会：尊重、陪伴、善待</span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 32px;\">给予孩子爱的教育、美的教育、善的教育</span></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7939,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492496714000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Leo","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaSic0ds8BMCibGZ2OUAZx2wvLS7l0JfCujUnFH561QnYtbqvZs2sAcicsmYHVHeJSgYia20o2R8WfC0mn/0","content":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">活动策划主管与活动策划执行</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">活动策划主管：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">1.规划全年活动安排；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">2.确定每个活动是否策划，策划方向；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">3.与策划执行进行对接，传递活动的意义；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">4.监管活动策划与执行过程；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">5.检验最终活动成果。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">活动策划执行员（活动总控）：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">1.明确活动目的；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">2.安排团队成员各司其职；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">3.安排活动的宣传与招生；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">4.活动执行方案制定，物资准备；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">5.活动参与客户的服务。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7935,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492488436000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"博学笃志","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/hglMZuicA3iauTIlciaKXMtjGcyXgjKvljRv5hsGdS0pUiaecGsLTmju6ib8JdHpQwqZqXeovGLB8HRWVxBjq0BaZpicsLFdj3dfibia/0","content":"<p>&nbsp;我选择妻子的角色，<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">与我对应的那个社会角色是丈夫。对方并不明确他的角色认知，需要我帮助他澄清：</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 28px; background-color: transparent;\">1、关心妻子；</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 28px; background-color: transparent;\">2、照顾</span><span style=\"line-height: 28px; background-color: transparent;\">孩子 ；</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 28px; background-color: transparent;\">3、承担家庭经济压力‘；</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 28px; background-color: transparent;\">4、承担家务。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7890,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492431818000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"放开那个小Joy","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEqUiaGZPHI2ga7E0gShutjcib8GKdDjQktSAdYIKa4icV4VOImzSz7BGe9nzia5iaxFMrTH0qEmSRDnhN/0","content":"之前有和老板沟通过，直接领导和跨级领导，区别是直接领导更关心下属是否稳定能完成交办的事情即可，而跨级领导更专注结果","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7623,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492047434000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"锦慕兰","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-11","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaS3skBBT8HsSPCyTJe0kT5cTVYOdIHeuEGdvfS3eHvDbZuYZcRIMxiaz0lVQjiadx2BdTtgw0bzCCn0/0","content":"<p>妻子－丈夫</p><p>对丈夫角色的理解：</p><p>1）有家庭责任感：凡事以家为单位考虑，而不再以个人的喜好为主要依据。</p><p>2）有主见，有担当：家里需要做出重大决定的时候，能给出自己的意见，并结合考虑家人的意见，关键时候能拍板，并承担后果。</p><p>3）做好父母和妻子之间的沟通桥梁，有能力化解两个家庭之间的矛盾。</p><p>4）对妻子体贴，主动承担部分家务，没有大男子主义倾向；尊重孩子的选择，没有家长制的作风。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7512,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491886131000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"球状闪电","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-10","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLCPB8632Nxuia6CTs7I9LbKdkG6NPFtfP9L6Fr0dibaM7qSNgmGkpnL2Ac6YEAnVmEsBzHAbu4IicjuQ/0","content":"单身狗设想一下以后如何跟未来的老公如何沟通“丈夫”这一角色：<div>1.提问：如，他先说他自己觉得他作为老公，最终要&amp;最不重要、他做得最好&amp;最不好的，然后我谈我的看法，两相对比。</div><div>2.观察：双方父母、共同的朋友的丈夫是怎样的，对比我们自己。</div><div>3.对比：同样是职场人士，老婆我VS老公在家庭生活（如做家务、带小孩等等），不要求完全对等，但是家庭是需要双方都投入时间精力去经营的。<br><div><br></div></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7473,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491831092000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"lanlan","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-09","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoABxary8VgXcewR1AmF19vgqh1yjicvfMjehwnN9BCtpicJfHXYmt3tEsP23v1u2lfVGIFicncrooia2/0","content":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 作为项目负责人，我对下属的角色认知是：</p><p>（1）参与讨论项目方案，了解项目整体框架和设计；</p><p>（2）接受研发任务，提出负责模块的详细设计和实现方法；</p><p>（3）完成模块开发，以及模块单元测试；</p><p>（4）参与整个系统的联调，进行模块的功能完善工作；</p><p>（5）提交模块开发的文档。<br><br></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7435,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491740879000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"丫头","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-04","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEpzDs95QValAW9uMicuTVwt7LGRUyD6sukUbZL6y2iaJDFgmHFGKtq1r6uWRta02dBqt8Wzyu3YPXW/0","content":"我选择的角色是妻子，与我对应的角色是丈夫<div>&nbsp;1️⃣一件事情，确保两个人同一认为范围内沟通</div><div>2️⃣针对异议，针对事情本身进行沟通，双方均表达对这件事情的看法，然后尽可能寻求双方都认可的解决方案</div><div>3️⃣尊重对方的工作，生活选择，给以充分的自由空间和选择度</div><div><br></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7176,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491284615000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"施伟","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-03","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEo9P2jC2S2gtzmiaPWycP2Fd6c8Lvunc8sP0iapaIrzxCur3tMr7Bia6kYfGXE4Pn3CLxmAUW8nr6ZK/0","content":"我来体验一下老板的角色，我认为我的员工要热爱工作，要不断学习知识和技术，来武装自己，习得东西都是你自己的，这一切不是给我学的，到任何地方都是你自己力量，决定你的价值，也是你值多少钱啊！","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7138,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491217855000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"迷迭香","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-31","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6bWV5FUyboCIOk2icGvegOZ7qmwDXVPlm0pmyu0tuemmkIaDqE1O6xCdX1tVMLNtwTvuVYVOMKQG3A/0","content":"我和我男朋友对他即将承担的角色（丈夫）进行了沟通，认知基本是一致的。在工作上:积极上进，为创造更好的生活奋斗。在生活上:孝敬老人，承担起“桥梁”角色，充分发挥沟通协调作用；抚养后代，承担好为人父的责任，不能把孩子推给别人撒手不管；理解和尊重妻子，给予对方信任和支持，共同面对家庭琐事，遇到问题商量着解决，能共苦可同甘。这些基本是我提出的要求，男友表示认可，想法一致。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5516,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490965666000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"王佳","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-31","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AywoaJCYTv4hicL3wib7fApyhLPNJiaroIhefibZ5St8K9AWkmRhDQ3astuE22Q5cDMLXKe5anwROuryia/0","content":"父母角色。\n我认为父母\n1.应在情感上与孩子独立，不能将情感寄托在孩子身上。\n2.当孩子成家后，应经济独立，不再供给孩子，也不得干涉孩子的经济情况。\n3.心态开放，对新事物有好奇心。\n\n父母对其角色的认知：\n1.孩子即使90岁，也是孩子。\n2.自己是老古董，没能力学习新知识。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6485,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490927276000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":false},"code":200}
